  • end collection:

  • frequency: 30 Hz
  • flux: 216 US gal/min

Notes:

  • floc was prepared in a concentrated mixture, then added close to the flume bed in the test section downstream of LISST device
  • floc included 155.5 g of kaolinite and 31.1 g of NaCl
  • some floc settled in the test bed where the mixture was added; otherwise, little settling
